1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:47,220
(Great Buddha Temple)

4
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,880
This temple is tucked away so deep.

5
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,520
No wonder so few worshippers come here.

6
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:56,640
But why would Noble Consort Xiao
invite you to pray here?

7
00:00:57,150 --> 00:00:58,710
I barely have any dealings with her.

8
00:00:58,860 --> 00:00:59,750
I have no idea

9
00:00:59,750 --> 00:01:00,890
why she asked me to join her.

10
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:07,280
Could it be
because of Nanny Li's matter?

11
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,300
That happened a long time ago.

12
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:10,550
If she wanted to settle scores,

13
00:01:10,550 --> 00:01:11,430
why wait until today?

14
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,550
Strange acts often hide deeper motives.

15
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,150
Just keep your guard up later.

16
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:18,480
And I've heard

17
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,590
that Noble Consort Xiao
is no ordinary figure.

18
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,510
She started as a palace maid,

19
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:24,120
and rose all the way to noble consort.

20
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,640
We'd better tread carefully around her.

21
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,480
Mm.

22
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,640
Here they come.

23
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,430
Such a grand display.

24
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:58,300
(Great Buddha Temple)

25
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:00,070
Let's go.

26
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,430
Greetings to you, Your Highness.

27
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,280
Qingyao,

28
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,360
we are all family.

29
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,750
No need to be so formal.

30
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,590
Thank you, Your Highness.

31
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:22,280
Seeing in person is truly
beyond hearing tales.

32
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:26,080
You are indeed

33
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:27,700
as beautiful

34
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:29,090
and intelligent as the legends say,

35
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:31,840
instantly winning people's hearts
at first sight.

36
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,280
You are flattering me.

37
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,910
Who in the world does not know

38
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:39,470
that 'peerless grace'

39
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,710
is a phrase for none but you?

40
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,800
Between us, there's no need
for courtesy.

41
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:45,870
Let's go.

42
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,770
I'll take you to the temple
to offer prayers.

43
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:52,630
Though the temple is rather quiet,

44
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,960
it is said to be most effective.

45
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,470
Please.

46
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:22,560
Qingyao,

47
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:25,150
you've been married to the Crown Prince
for some time now.

48
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:28,800
I've been occupied caring
for His Majesty and Huan.

49
00:03:29,430 --> 00:03:30,750
At last, today,

50
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:32,180
I finally get the chance to see you.

51
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:36,840
It was my oversight.

52
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:40,310
I should have entered the Palace
to pay respects to His Majesty,

53
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:41,280
and the other consorts.

54
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,910
Instead, I trouble you to come
in person.

55
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:45,140
Think nothing of it.

56
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:48,620
His Majesty has been gravely ill
recently.

57
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:52,540
He seldom has moments of clarity.

58
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,560
He likely hasn't the strength
to meet you.

59
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,700
My reason for leaving the Palace
this time

60
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:58,660
is also to pray
for His Majesty's recovery.

61
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:01,340
You are most considerate.

62
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:03,140
However,

63
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:06,380
I just don't know what illness
His Majesty is suffering from.

64
00:04:08,940 --> 00:04:10,580
The ailment is most peculiar.

65
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,300
Even the imperial physician

66
00:04:12,460 --> 00:04:14,060
cannot determine the cause.

67
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:18,460
Now the Crown Prince
governs on His Majesty's behalf.

68
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:21,260
My son Ling Huan is still young.

69
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:28,660
In the future, he will need you
and the Crown Prince

70
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:30,140
to look after him more.

71
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:34,460
(Why would Noble Consort Xiao
say this to Qingyao?)

72
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:36,700
(Could she be testing)

73
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:38,820
(the Crown Prince's stance
on the Second Prince?)

74
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:45,180
The Second Prince
is the Crown Prince's only brother.

75
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:47,420
Family members

76
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:49,180
should naturally help each other.

77
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:53,780
You're the Crown Princess's
personal guard?

78
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:56,140
May I know your name?

79
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:58,860
When asking someone's name,

80
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:00,740
it's proper to give your own first.

81
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:05,460
Wu Yun.

82
00:05:07,100 --> 00:05:08,180
Wu Yun.

83
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:09,980
Wu Yun.

84
00:05:11,540 --> 00:05:12,380
I'm not telling you.

85
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:15,740
Interesting.

86
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:18,300
You look a bit familiar.

87
00:05:18,700 --> 00:05:20,900
Have we met before?

88
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:22,420
(Not good.)

89
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:24,220
(Could he know Shiyi?)

90
00:05:26,820 --> 00:05:28,640
My face is plain and ordinary.

91
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:30,250
You'll find many like it on the street.

92
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:31,500
So it's normal to feel familiar.

93
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,460
You're being too modest.

94
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:39,780
Not only is your appearance
extraordinary,

95
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:41,740
but your inner strength

96
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:44,020
is also renowned in the martial world.

97
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:47,740
Why not spar with me for a round?

98
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:50,180
You want to spar with me?

99
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:51,700
Mm.

100
00:05:52,700 --> 00:05:55,260
Then I wonder

101
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:56,980
what your ranking
in the martial world is.

102
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:00,440
I'm not interested in participating
in those boring rankings.

103
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,860
I only know that there is
a Wind and Rain Pavilion,

104
00:06:03,460 --> 00:06:05,380
and inside it there is a killer
named Shiyi,

105
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,100
who is quite skilled.

106
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:09,460
(So he really has met Shiyi.)

107
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:11,140
(Could he be starting to suspect me?)

108
00:06:11,780 --> 00:06:12,860
It's a pity, though,

109
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:14,660
I only caught a glimpse

110
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:17,820
of that person among the crowd.

111
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,200
And didn't get the chance
to have a contest with him.

112
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:22,780
It seems

113
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:24,780
you have quite some faith

114
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:26,660
in your own abilities.

115
00:06:27,060 --> 00:06:29,300
I am ashamed of my inferiority.

116
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,040
Maybe another day.

117
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,270
Whether you're inferior or not,

118
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:32,350
we'll know once we compete.

119
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:35,780
As the Crown Princess,

120
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:39,060
it's your duty

121
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:40,420
to carry on the royal bloodline.

122
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:43,980
This temple is known
for its divine power.

123
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:47,940
I've already prayed to the Bodhisattva
on your behalf.

124
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:51,780
May you be blessed with a child soon.

125
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:54,780
(Is she afraid that Qingyao's pregnancy)

126
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,090
(would threaten the position
of the Second Prince?)

127
00:06:59,300 --> 00:07:00,180
To be honest with you,

128
00:07:01,260 --> 00:07:02,340
these past few days...

129
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:09,060
I've often felt nauseous and queasy.

130
00:07:09,940 --> 00:07:12,300
It feels as if I might be pregnant.

131
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:17,300
Truly?

132
00:07:17,940 --> 00:07:19,140
By all signs,

133
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:25,340
it's almost certain.

134
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,940
I really am getting old.

135
00:07:48,380 --> 00:07:49,860
After just this short while,

136
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:51,900
I already feel worn out.

137
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:53,740
Qingyao,

138
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:55,860
come with me to the back hall,

139
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:57,060
and rest for a moment.

140
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:11,580
What are you doing?

141
00:08:12,580 --> 00:08:13,500
Sorry.

142
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:14,990
I'm a bit obsessed with martial arts.

143
00:08:14,990 --> 00:08:17,220
Whenever I meet a master,
I can't resist sparring.

144
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,760
Noble Consort Xiao, what are you doing?

145
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:08,300
What do you think?

146
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,440
Naturally, ending your life.

147
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:14,020
I bear you no grudge.

148
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:15,380
Why do you wish to kill me?

149
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:17,600
Don't hold it against me.

150
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:20,820
Blame fate for giving you
the wrong birth.

151
00:09:21,580 --> 00:09:22,540
Rest assured.

152
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:24,540
I only seek your heart's blood.

153
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:26,420
You won't feel any pain.

154
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:31,460
You've lost.

155
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:35,340
Seems you're not the one
I'm searching for.

156
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:38,780
You truly wield great skill.

157
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:40,740
Why trouble yourself
with a nobody like me?

158
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:44,240
It's merely a friendly match.

159
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,420
Ah!

160
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:50,100
Gu Qingyao,

161
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:51,260
you've got some nerve.

162
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:53,660
Noble Consort Xiao,
you're not bad either.

163
00:09:53,980 --> 00:09:54,820
Qingyao.

164
00:09:58,420 --> 00:09:59,260
Are you alright?

165
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,790
- What are you doing?
- Are you alright?

166
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:08,740
Hurry and help me up.

167
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:10,860
It's nothing.

168
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:17,940
How did this happen?

169
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:20,340
That woman wants your life.

170
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:22,060
You were right after all.

171
00:10:22,540 --> 00:10:24,020
Unusual happenings often hide trouble.

172
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,890
What about your side?
How's the situation?

173
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:29,020
Her guard seems to know you.

174
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,580
He has likely grown suspicious.

175
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,580
Wu Yun,

176
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:37,020
you can't let them leave alive today.

177
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:41,460
What's going on?

178
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:42,700
Could it be

179
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:44,770
that you can't even handle them?

180
00:10:47,260 --> 00:10:48,100
Quiet!

181
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:00,540
He's strong.

182
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:04,060
Don't fight him head-on.

183
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:07,020
Use your wit instead.

184
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:13,540
Ah! Someone's been killed!

185
00:11:13,740 --> 00:11:15,460
- A murder!
- Someone's been killed!

186
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,660
There's been a killing over here!

187
00:11:17,660 --> 00:11:18,740
Something happened.

188
00:11:18,910 --> 00:11:20,500
Not the right time, let's go!

189
00:11:20,900 --> 00:11:22,060
There's been a killing here!

190
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:22,900
Go!

191
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:25,290
- Someone's been killed!
- Help!

192
00:11:28,260 --> 00:11:30,220
It's all right.

193
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:31,660
They're trying to kill us!

194
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:44,540
Choke you?

195
00:11:44,820 --> 00:11:46,100
She actually dared to choke you.

196
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:46,980
Where? Let me see.

197
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,300
It's nothing.

198
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:04,620
What about you?

199
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:07,300
How is the situation?

200
00:12:09,980 --> 00:12:12,100
That man named Wu Yun is not
to be underestimated,

201
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,900
and even if your internal strength
returns,

202
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:15,290
I doubt you could stand against him.

203
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:16,900
His moves are truly strange,

204
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:18,990
nothing like any martial art
from the Central Plains.

205
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:21,460
Before this,

206
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:23,340
had you ever heard of him?

207
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:24,900
No, never.

208
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:37,940
Oh right,

209
00:12:38,780 --> 00:12:41,700
have you ever offended
Noble Consort Xiao?

210
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:44,660
Of course not.

211
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:45,860
I've never even met her.

212
00:12:46,980 --> 00:12:49,340
Then why would she risk so much
to kill you?

213
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:52,940
I have no idea.

214
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:58,940
What if there is someone else
behind her?

215
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:01,140
If we act rashly now,

216
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:03,780
we'll fall right into their trap.

217
00:13:07,740 --> 00:13:08,580
Oh right,

218
00:13:09,140 --> 00:13:11,700
she said she wanted your heart's blood.

219
00:13:14,060 --> 00:13:15,140
My heart's blood?

220
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:16,140
Mm.

221
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:18,590
Why would she insist
on taking your heart's blood?

222
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:21,940
Do you know what that blood is used for?

223
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:31,780
Don't think about it.

224
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:33,580
What worries me more right now

225
00:13:33,580 --> 00:13:34,740
is not Noble Consort Xiao,

226
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:36,820
but the guard by her side.

227
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:39,620
You know what?

228
00:13:40,020 --> 00:13:41,020
Their relationship is not

229
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:42,340
that of master and servant at all.

230
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:43,740
It's very uncanny.

231
00:13:48,180 --> 00:13:49,860
Anyway, the whole thing
feels suspicious.

232
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:51,540
We need to get to the bottom of it.

233
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:56,540
There's one person,

234
00:13:57,900 --> 00:14:00,180
who might be able to figure out
these shady tricks.

235
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:14,340
♪When a breeze passes by♪

236
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:18,180
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

237
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:20,820
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

238
00:14:21,140 --> 00:14:24,300
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

239
00:14:24,660 --> 00:14:27,620
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

240
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:30,940
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

241
00:14:31,140 --> 00:14:33,860
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

242
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:37,660
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

243
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:39,420
♪I finally understood that truth♪

244
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:40,900
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

245
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:42,740
♪I lose my way in the night♪

246
00:14:42,740 --> 00:14:44,220
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

247
00:14:44,220 --> 00:14:45,900
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

248
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:48,860
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

249
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:51,740
♪For you and me to meet again♪

250
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:55,020
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

251
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:57,380
♪In the pouring rain♪

252
00:14:57,380 --> 00:15:01,740
♪As if you are still by my side♪
